      • findOwnNullabilityInfo

        public NullabilityAnnotationInfo findOwnNullabilityInfo(PsiModifierListOwner owner)
        Returns own nullability annotation info for given element. Returned annotation is not inherited and not container annotation for class/package. Still it could be inferred or external.
        Parameters:
        owner - element to find a nullability info for
        Returns:
        own nullability annotation info.

      • findExplicitNullability

        public NullabilityAnnotationInfo findExplicitNullability(PsiModifierListOwner owner)
        Returns information about explicit nullability annotation (without looking into external/inferred annotations, but looking into container annotations). This method is rarely useful in client code, it's designed mostly to aid the inference procedure.
        Parameters:
        owner - element to get the info about
        Returns:
        the annotation info or null if no explicit annotation found
